        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued March 31 at 4:01PM EDT until March 31 at 7:00PM EDT by NWS Greenville-Spartanburg SC</headline>
        <description>SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 87 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 7 PM EDT THIS
EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN NORTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 7 COUNTIES

IN PIEDMONT NORTH CAROLINA

CABARRUS              CLEVELAND             GASTON
LINCOLN               MECKLENBURG           UNION NC

IN WESTERN NORTH CAROLINA

RUTHERFORD

IN SOUTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 7 COUNTIES

IN UPSTATE SOUTH CAROLINA

CHEROKEE              CHESTER               GREENWOOD
LAURENS               SPARTANBURG           UNION SC
YORK

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BLACKSTOCK, CATAWBA, CHARLOTTE,
CHESTER, CLINTON, CONCORD, CORNWELL, CROUSE, FOREST CITY,
GAFFNEY, GASTONIA, GREAT FALLS, HUNTERSVILLE, INDIAN TRAIL,
KANNAPOLIS, KINGS MOUNTAIN, LAURENS, LINCOLNTON, MATTHEWS,
MONARCH MILLS, MONROE, NINETY SIX, ROCK HILL, RUTHERFORDTON,
SHELBY, SPARTANBURG, SPINDALE, TRINITY, UNION, WARE SHOALS,
AND WEDDINGTON.
</description>
